# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Frontend environment configuration (.env)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The build scripts (`build.sh` / `build-debug.sh`) automatically source this
# file and export all non-comment lines as environment variables so that they
# are available at *compile-time* for `wasm-pack`.
#
# Google Sign-In --------------------------------------------------------------
# 1)  GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID      – OAuth 2.0 *Client ID* obtained from Google Cloud
#                             Console.
# 2)  GOOGLE_AUTH_ENABLED   – Toggle that controls whether the sign-in overlay
#                             appears in the UI.  Accepted truthy values are
#                             `1`, `true`, `yes` – anything else disables the
#                             overlay.
#
# If you want the auth overlay disabled by default simply set
# `GOOGLE_AUTH_ENABLED=false`.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Example – enable auth
# GOOGLE_AUTH_ENABLED=true
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=1234567890-abcxyz.apps.googleusercontent.com

# Example – disable auth (but keep the client ID defined for later)
# GOOGLE_AUTH_ENABLED=false
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=1234567890-abcxyz.apps.googleusercontent.com
